=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"ae8f3a773700313f3a5c25b7ab2aa67cee2208d4","tid":1630493,"uid":46966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:16:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇佢地想企美國定中國啦<br />\n上次美議員先出聲 再封未來實封殺你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f950385064cc4bc742a6aa6e54639050afa7370","tid":1630493,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:16:43.000Z","msg":"【政府製造經濟危機】以最和理非既方式 擊敗港共<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630641\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630641</a>"},{"pid":"2ac38474924d3871d2328894a239fb5afaa6e43b","tid":1630493,"uid":281029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4fdf0382f15c58828044bd325bf854aa35877c0","tid":1630493,"uid":59764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7zPE526.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7zPE526.png&h=30485c63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDKLM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/sNXAqyuBv2Pb80MMlc3_Gw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2FsNXAqyuBv2Pb80MMlc3_Gw&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6p2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=10f13ce8\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/sNXAqyuBv2Pb80MMlc3_Gw</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:21:08.000Z","msg":"東隧、紅隧、西隧九龍入口、大埔廣福油站<br />\n觀塘道大搜捕，搵間餐廳坐陣先啦 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/8413498154/permalink/10156986489413155/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.